<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[١٨٧٥ - د هـ ن]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>ادَّهنَ/ ادَّهنَ بـ يدَّهن، ادِّهانًا، فهو مُدَّهِن، والمفعول مُدَّهَن به<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• ادَّهن الشَّخصُ:</span> تطلَّى بالدُّهْن.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">• ادَّهن بالشَّيء:</span> طلى نفسَه به.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>